Your #1 Love Type: ENFP

The Inspirer In love, you are passionate and eager to develop a strong bond. For you, sex should be playful, creative, and affectionate. Overall, you are perceptive and bring out the best in your partner. However, you tend to hold on to bad relationships after they've turned bad. Best matches: INTJ and INFJ

Your #2 Love Type: ENFJ

The Giver In love, you give your all and feel guilty when relationships fail. For you, sex is not seperate from love and caring. Overall, you are humorous, giving, and motivational. However, you tend to be over-protective and critical of your partner. Best matches: INFP or ISFP

Your #3 Love Type: ENTP

The Visionary In love, you are always trying to improve and grow your relationship. For you, sex should be a spontaneous adventure. Overall, you are magnetic, inspiring, and a charmer. However, you tend to get bored and want to change partners frequently. Best matches: INFJ and INTJ

Your #4 Love Type: ESFP

The Performer In love, you relish every moment and tend to get caught up in passion. For you, sex is how you get in touch with all your senses. Overall, you are creative, popular, and flexible. However, you tend to dislike criticism and avoid any conflict. Best matches: ISTJ or ISFJ

Your #5 Love Type: INFP

The Idealist In love, you crave a long term, harmonious relationship. For you, sex doesn't come quickly - it takes time for you to open up. Overall, you are supportive, nurturing, and expressive. However, you tend to be shy and protective of your personal space. Best matches: ENFJ and ESFJ
What's Your Love Type?
You Are a Hunter Soul
You are driven and ambitious - totally self motiviated to succeed Actively working to acheive what you want, you are skillful in many areas. You are a natural predator with strong instincts ... and more than a little demanding. You are creative, energetic, and an extremely powerful force. An outdoors person, you like animals and relate to them better than people. You tend to have an explosive personality, but also a good sense of humor. People sometimes see you as arrogant or a know it all. You tend to be a bit of a loner, though you hate to be alone. Souls you are most compatible with: Seeker Soul and Peacemaker Soul

In love, you feel the most alive when things are straight-forward, and you're told that you're loved.

so many mem'ries of loving legit
so many times i thought, "hey! this is it!"
so many times have i traveled that highway
just to be left, all alone, on the sideway

mem'ries of kisses in my hair
mem'ries of first-hugs while aware
mem'ries of sadness, mem'ries of joy
i remember each one, every single damn boy

there was mathew kinni,
my pre-school crush
there was abel and justin
damn how much i would blush

there was colter...
then jason - 
still not sure who stood who up -
there was corey...
and justin - 
one day he just stopped showing up.

i remember every face, avery voice, avery day...
i remember every pain as they each walked away...

then the crushes ended, and the courting began
there was ryan walsh - though technically i got asked by dan
then came in love being in love matt
he really was sweet even though he always spat

there was sean - still not quite sure where that stood
but, well, while it was, i know it was good
then along came dave, just looking for his first kiss
i guess that was dumb - i got a quick dismiss

then there was ryan, insane yet so sweet
so tall and so skinny, i once danced on his feet
it lasted eight months, and another three days
then it was over, but i'll cherish always

then there almost was paxton - all mushrooms and green
but when i found what he said, well, i made quite a scene.

...then there was Lloyd - so sngry and set
the closest to heart, the nearest end yet.

every damn one, i thought was the last
i let them all in, then watched them turn into my past

i remember each hug, i remember such bliss...
i remember each dance, i remember each kiss...
and that's where they'll stay
locked away, out of view
No longer to say:
"Kat, I love you."

-glitch

The saddest thing
I've ever seen
I saw at Disneyland
Two parents talking
On their cells
Each held a young girl's hand

A family vacation
A family escape
Though they walked so close together
Couldn't feel farther away

In the girl I saw our future
In her parents saw the why
I saw a future devoid of love
The image made me want to cry

They were there with their daughter
They were there with who they "love"
Wonder how much they bought her
To replace a simple hug

I wanted to cry for that little girl
I wanted to cry for me
I don't know what's become of the world
But it seems love's earned a fee

The saddest thing
I'll ever see
I saw at Disneyland
Two parents talking
On their cells
Oblivious to a child's sweet hand.

-glitch


Yesterday:

-Kyle, friend of two years, kissed me. He said he loved me, that i was         amazing, and that he wanted to see me everyday. I think I might care about him too, but, due to other factors, (such as Lloyd and my grandpa - some of factor explained below) I can't really be sure.

-My grandpa had surgery at the emergency room in Kaiser. He had a hole in his intestines. You have no idea how hard it is to see a guy that's tough as shit, and never lets you see any of his personal crap, lying, helpless, in a giant diaper with an oxygen mask and a morphine pump.

-I told Lloyd I might have feelings for Kyle - we ended up splitting cuz "we weren't compatible anyway"(???)I realized I misjudged a lot about Lloyd, and I told him so, but, like it says in a poem i wrote about it, it doesn't change anything.

*note: do not expect me to talk about any of this shit for awhile - i really don't think i can yet, and if you ask, i'll either end up telling you more than you really want to know, or i'll end up hitting you, storming off, and apologizing profusely later on. don't ask, don't die.

are the girl in the little black number that no one seems to know, the eternal
mystery girl. You make it a point to never let anyone know more about you than

gone the next leaving them in wonder of who you really are. A mature and normally
calm individual, quiet and enjoy spending many hours of the day on your own,
most likely preferring night to day . You love the dark and some may find you a
